          "text": "Because the real world keeps happening. (pause) Some \u201cstandard\u201d stamps can\u2019t be sourced in time. (pause) So substitutions got written down. (pause) And everyone acts shocked we admitted it. (pause) Pick from the board or don\u2019t file.",
